@startuml
title Finding Broken Access Control: Practical Testing Workflow

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam defaultFontName Helvetica
skinparam defaultFontSize 12

start
:Enumerate endpoints\n(UI + API);
:Identify sensitive actions\n(read/write/admin);
:Capture baseline request\n(as authorized user);
:Mutate control points\n(id, role, endpoint,\nmethod, body fields);
if (Unauthorized data/function?) then (yes)
  :Document steps + impact;
  :Propose fix\n(central AuthZ,\nownership checks,\ndeny-by-default);
  :Retest after remediation;
else (no)
  :Record as not vulnerable\nfor this case;
endif
stop

legend right
Start/end visible; decisions labeled; steps concise.
endlegend
@enduml
